properties.media:imagetext:
Prior to Takeoff
Premium champagne
After Takeoff
Cocktail or beverage of your choice
Cured olives with herbs
Roasted cashews
Appetizers
Scottish smoked salmon, longtail shrimp,
mesquite-marinated chicken breast and asparagus spears,
garnished with strawberry and kiwi,
served with wasabi sauce
Salad
Assortment of salad leaves,
garnished with cucumber slices, radishes and croutons
Choice of balsamic vinaigrette or low-fat blue cheese dressing
Entrées
Filet Mignon
Served with bordelaise sauce and Anna potatoes
Veal Rib Chop
Served with a broiled tomato and duchess sweet potatoes
Grilled Breast of Chicken
Boneless, served with forestière sauce, and new potato wedges with rosemary
Fillet of Salmon
Grilled, enhanced by printemps sauce with scallions,
accompanied by saffron rice
Medallions of Lobster and Chateaubriand
Served chilled with smoked turkey,
artichoke salad and rémoulade sauce
Hot entrées will be accompanied by green beans with red peppers
Dinner rolls and butter will be served with all entrées
Please accept our apology if your first entrée preference is not available.
Passengers who prefer more time for work or sleep may request
our Royal Ambassador Express Service.
Dessert
Assortment of seasonal fruit and International cheeses
Häagen-Dazs vanilla frozen yogurt and chocolate brownie loaf
Chocolate sauce
Accompanied with coffee, decaffeinated coffee or tea
Continental Breakfast Buffet
Duty Free shopping available on today's flight.
D65E 1/95
